{
  "stem": "734.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They didn't give you anything, whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This was considered a short ride.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, 24 hours, it's nothing, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course not, nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These cars were sealed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the little windows that they had were wired.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No, you couldn't or anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the population wasn't so interested in any of that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, they had no interest to keep contact with the deported Jews.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You probably remember--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm sure they were aware, yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the countryside was kind of empty.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But you couldn't see very  much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, there were not many people around to begin with.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was wintertime.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But nobody worked out in the fields.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so it was desolate, really.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The whole-- And we arrived at Mauthausen-- at Majdanek.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And, of course, the scene was the same as any arrival.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You went through the showers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was morning, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was like early morning when we arrived.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were brought into the showers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we didn't know whether they were showers or not.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I do remember-- because, at that time, we  had already heard enough stories about the gas chambers and, and all that, the way they fool you with it, bring you into the showers.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You think it's going to-- instead of water, you get gas.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Registration?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very simple.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You came-- You went through a line.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you were shaven, and your hair was cut clean.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You had no hair left.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they-- You simply followed-- they show you where to go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Eventually, you wound up in-- you left all your clothes off.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You were just like naked, in the nude.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You went into this huge place, which was the shower room.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I do remember I-- I was able to take, with me, my forged ID card.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
